1. *Njihov* dom je velik i udoban. (Their house is big and comfortable.)
2. Oni su *njihov* dom napravili sami. (They made their house themselves.)
3. *Njihova* deca su veoma živahna. (Their children are very lively.)
4. Oni su ponosni na *njihovo* ponašanje. (They are proud of their behaviour.)
5. *Njihovo* putovanje je bilo dugo. (Their journey was long.)
6. Oni su ponosni na *njihove* uspehe. (They are proud of their achievements.)